column2: SELECT    m.CATID, m.RA AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1,    n.objid, n.distance,   o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,   o.fiberMag_u, o.fiberMag_g, o.fiberMag_r, o.fiberMag_i, o.fiberMag_z into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.sami_gama_coords AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
